package.name: sheadawson/quickaddnew
package.description: A decorator for form fields that manage object relationships, to allow adding a new object on the fly through a dialog window. It can handle has_one, has_many or many_many relationships. At the moment it has been tested / works on DropdownField and ListboxField. It works both in the CMS and in the frontend.
